TextMate Hotkeys
================

^ Cmd T				Select bundle tiem
Fn <enter>			Open current URL	(Hyperlink helper bundle)
Cmd Y				Git commands


## Macros
isoD ⇥				Insert date


## Text
Cmd |               Filter thru command
^ Cmd Shift T       Tabs/Spaces converions
            1       Convert spaces to tabs
            2       Convert tabs to spaces
            3       Convert spaces to tabs (estimate indents)


## Navigate
Cmd L           Jump to line…
Cmd Shift T     Jump to symbol…
Cmd J           Jump to selection


## View
Cmd +/-/0       Font size: increase/decrease/default
Cmd Option I    Show/Hide invisible characters (editor pane need to have focus)
Cmd Option W    Toggle soft wrap
F1              Fold current block


## File
^ Cmd Option D  Toggle file pane sidebar
Cmd Option I    Show/Hide hidden files (file pane need to have focus)

^ Cmd N         New file in enclosing folder of selected item
Cmd Shift N     New folder in enclosing folder of selected item

Cmd ↑			Make enclosing folder the file sidebar pane root
^ Cmd R			Select currently opened file
Cmd Shift A		Select none in file sidebar


## ⌘ ⌥ ⇧ ⇥ ↩ ↑ ↓ ← → ##



